@AppointWeb.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:8080

### Catalog
GET {{AppointWeb.Api_HostAddress}}/api/catalog
Accept: application/json

###
GET {{AppointWeb.Api_HostAddress}}/api/catalog/{{providerId}}/{{serviceId}}/slots?from=2026-07-08T00:00:00Z&to=2026-07-15T00:00:00Z
Accept: application/json

### Auth
POST {{AppointWeb.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "customer@example.com",
  "password": "your-password"
